Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:08.32,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Lelouch went to a resort when you were both young, and that's where you met each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:12.22,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we really haven't spent that much time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:16.26,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you stop speaking in such a formal manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.35,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,We are in the same grade after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.09,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:21.73,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.29,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.00,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,But I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.60,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first person I met who knows a bit about Lelouch's childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:32.57,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,That guy never says anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:35.72,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Can you pass me that 12 millimeter wrench?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.51,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need an 11 millimeter one for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:39.07,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:40.60,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,You are sure familiar with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.10,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,The RR1200 from BMC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.34,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is a nice bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.85,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:51.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Before I joined the army, the person who took care of me rode this model.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.73,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,My job was to service and wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:56.08,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I was told, "Gosh, I'll kill you if you ride it without permission!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.64,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I was never allowed to ride it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.55,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:01.35,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,"Gosh"? That sounds feminine... was it a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:01.91,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:02.91,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,A girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:03.72,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.72,0:01:05.19,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Then... your elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.68,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:07.97,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,You are terribly wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:10.27,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:13.55,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the person who took care of me has already...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.06,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... this is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:17.92,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,I asked something inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:20.46,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's just the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:22.37,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Then... what about your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:23.43,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:27.56,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,The unit I'm assigned to is currently stationed at the university across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:30.09,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm living at the lodging house there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:32.95,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you stay at the one in the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:35.10,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a roommate in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:36.21,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,If it's fine with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:38.88,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But I have my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:42.26,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I made the choice myself to join the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:44.41,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:49.19,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1040)}Yes. But thanks, Rivalz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:58.03,CG ON,Cecil,0000,0000,0000,,Lloyd-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.53,CG ON,Cecil,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and tidy up your documents!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.91,CG ON,Cecil,0000,0000,0000,,The luggage that was sent over hasn't been sorted either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:05.97,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave all the stuff here to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:08.30,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,You should know my work style by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:12.36,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about how many years it's been since we met each other at the university's laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.85,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,That is... Well... now that I think about it, it's been way too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.53,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,You really like it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.15,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:24.61,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I... erm... don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.37,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I'm referring to research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:29.58,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I understand! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:34.63,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to His Highness Schneizel that we're able to do anything we want here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.46,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.96,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're trying to solve the equation for the Surge Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.22,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:48.44,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, is it okay for all the general affairs of this Technological Department of Special Dispatch Envoys to come under my command?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.74,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.21,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Suzaku, reporting back, awaiting orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.75,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun, you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.47,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,You must say, "I'm back" at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.05,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But if I say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:01.18,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.16,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:06.10,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,In here, put military and social ranking aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.14,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:08.64,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.85,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Then Suzaku-kun, why don't you try and say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.66,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.62,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Treat it as if you have just returned to your own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.52,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,My own home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:23.25,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. After all, this place is like our home, isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.25,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.10,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Say it louder and with more energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.17,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.81,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:36.88,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,4590)}Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.31,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
